## 7. REQUIRED FILES FOR A NEW PROVIDER PACKAGE

```
packages/your-provider/
├── package.json                    # As above
├── tsconfig.json                   # Extends @vercel/ai-tsconfig
├── tsconfig.build.json             # Override composite: false
├── tsup.config.ts                  # Build configuration
├── vitest.node.config.js           # Node.js test environment
├── vitest.edge.config.js           # Edge runtime test environment
├── turbo.json                       # Extends root turbo
├── README.md                        # Provider documentation
├── CHANGELOG.md                     # Changelog (auto-generated by changesets)
├── src/
│   ├── index.ts                    # Main export file
│   ├── version.ts                  # Version constant
│   ├── your-provider.ts            # Main provider implementation
│   ├── your-provider-types.ts      # Type definitions (LanguageModelV3, etc.)
│   ├── your-provider-chat-options.ts
│   ├── your-provider-error.ts
│   ├── __fixtures__/               # Test response fixtures
│   │   ├── response-text.json
│   │   └── response-streaming.chunks.txt
│   └── *.test.ts                   # Test files
└── docs/                           # (Created at pack time from content/)
    └── XX-your-provider.mdx        # (Copied from content/providers/)
```

