# Plan: Add `@ai-sdk/pixel-art` Provider

## Context

The Vercel AI SDK uses a layered provider architecture where each AI service gets its own package under `packages/<name>`. We need to add a fictional **PixelArt** provider that exclusively supports image generation via the `ImageModelV3` interface. The provider must follow the exact same conventions as existing providers such as `@ai-sdk/fal` and `@ai-sdk/togetherai`, so it integrates cleanly into the monorepo build system.

The provider will:
- Export a `createPixelArt` factory function (and a pre-built `pixelArt` default instance)
- Use base URL `https://api.pixelart.ai/v1`
- Support provider-specific image settings: `style` (`"pixel"` | `"retro"` | `"8bit"`) and `pixelDensity` (number)
- Throw `NoSuchModelError` for language model and embedding model requests
- Only create new files — no changes to existing provider packages

---

## Critical Files to Create

```
packages/pixel-art/
├── package.json
├── tsconfig.json
├── tsconfig.build.json
├── tsup.config.ts
├── vitest.node.config.js
├── vitest.edge.config.js
└── src/
    ├── index.ts
    ├── version.ts
    ├── pixel-art-provider.ts
    ├── pixel-art-image-model.ts
    ├── pixel-art-image-settings.ts
    ├── pixel-art-image-options.ts
    └── pixel-art-image-model.test.ts
```

**File to modify:**
- `tsconfig.json` (repo root) — add `{ "path": "packages/pixel-art" }` in alphabetical order (after `packages/perplexity`, before `packages/provider`)

---

## Step-by-Step Implementation

### Step 1 — `packages/pixel-art/package.json`

Mirror `packages/fal/package.json` exactly, changing:
- `"name"`: `"@ai-sdk/pixel-art"`
- `"version"`: `"0.0.0"`
- Remove the `"prepack"/"postpack"` scripts (no MDX doc to copy yet)
- Keep all scripts, exports, dependencies, devDependencies, peerDependencies

```json
{
  "name": "@ai-sdk/pixel-art",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "license": "Apache-2.0",
  "sideEffects": false,
  "main": "./dist/index.js",
  "module": "./dist/index.mjs",
  "types": "./dist/index.d.ts",
  "files": ["dist/**/*", "src", "!src/**/*.test.ts", "!src/**/*.test-d.ts", "!src/**/__snapshots__", "!src/**/__fixtures__", "CHANGELOG.md", "README.md"],
  "scripts": {
    "build": "pnpm clean && tsup --tsconfig tsconfig.build.json",
    "build:watch": "pnpm clean && tsup --watch",
    "clean": "del-cli dist *.tsbuildinfo",
    "type-check": "tsc --build",
    "test": "pnpm test:node && pnpm test:edge",
    "test:update": "pnpm test:node -u",
    "test:watch": "vitest --config vitest.node.config.js",
    "test:edge": "vitest --config vitest.edge.config.js --run",
    "test:node": "vitest --config vitest.node.config.js --run"
  },
  "exports": {
    "./package.json": "./package.json",
    ".": { "types": "./dist/index.d.ts", "import": "./dist/index.mjs", "require": "./dist/index.js" }
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "@ai-sdk/provider": "workspace:*",
