```

### Step 5 — `packages/pixel-art/vitest.node.config.js` and `vitest.edge.config.js`

Identical to `packages/fal/vitest.node.config.js` / `.edge.config.js` (just change environment and package reference — both already use `packageJson.version` dynamic import).

### Step 6 — `src/version.ts`

```ts
