## Utility Reuse

| Utility | Source | Used for |
|---|---|---|
| `postJsonToApi` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | HTTP POST to image generation endpoint |
| `createJsonResponseHandler` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Parse successful JSON response |
| `createJsonErrorResponseHandler` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Parse error JSON response |
| `combineHeaders` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Merge config headers + per-call headers |
| `resolve` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Resolve `Resolvable<Headers>` from config |
| `parseProviderOptions` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Validate `providerOptions.pixelart` against Zod schema |
| `loadApiKey` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Load API key from options or `PIXELART_API_KEY` env |
| `withoutTrailingSlash` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Normalize base URL |
| `withUserAgentSuffix` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Add SDK version to User-Agent |
| `lazySchema` / `zodSchema` | `@ai-sdk/provider-utils` | Lazy Zod schema for provider options |
| `NoSuchModelError` | `@ai-sdk/provider` | Throw for unsupported model types |
| `ImageModelV3` / `ProviderV3` | `@ai-sdk/provider` | Core interfaces to implement |

---

## Verification

1. **Build**: `cd packages/pixel-art && pnpm build` — should produce `dist/index.js`, `dist/index.mjs`, `dist/index.d.ts`
2. **Type-check**: `pnpm type-check:full` from repo root — should pass with no errors (verifies the new package is correctly wired in root `tsconfig.json`)
3. **Tests**: `cd packages/pixel-art && pnpm test` — all test cases should pass
4. **Smoke test**: Create a test script that imports `createPixelArt` from the built package and calls `pixelArt.image('pixelart/standard')` — verify it returns an `ImageModelV3` instance; verify `pixelArt.languageModel('x')` throws `NoSuchModelError`

